 "(4)", "bbox": [162.5, 973.9, 186.8, 994.7]}, {"text": "Included in other non-current liabilities on the consolidated balance sheet.", "bbox": [204.2, 973.9, 822.2, 994.7]}, {"text": "(5)", "bbox": [162.5, 998.9, 186.8, 1019.7]}, {"text": "The carrying amount of the debt instrument is presented net of the debt issuance costs. Refer to Note 11,", "bbox": [204.2, 998.9, 1075.9, 1019.7]}, {"text": "“Debt”, for gross carrying amounts.", "bbox": [204.2, 1023.9, 503.1, 1044.7]}, {"text": "The Company values its financial instruments using an industry standard market approach, in which prices", "bbox": [204.2, 1077.1, 1095.0, 1097.9]}, {"text": "and other relevant information is generated by market transactions involving identical or comparable assets or", "bbox": [162.5, 1102.1, 1081.0, 1122.9]}, {"text": "liabilities. No financial instruments were recognized using unobservable inputs.", "bbox": [162.5, 1127.1, 828.0, 1147.9]}, {"text": "Interest rate swaps were measured at fair value using quoted market prices for the swap interest rate indexes", "bbox": [204.2, 1180.3, 1106.8, 1201.2]}, {"text": "over the term of the swap discounted to present value versus the fixed rate of the contract. The interest rate caps", "bbox": [162.5, 1205.3, 1096.4, 1226.2]}, {"text": "were measured at fair value using implied volatility rates of each individual caplet and the yield curve for the", "bbox": [162.5, 1230.3, 1074.0, 1251.2]}, {"text": "related periods. The estimated fair value of the Company’s term loans was based on information provided by the", "bbox": [162.5, 1255.3, 1102.7, 1276.2]}, {"text": "agent under the Company’s senior secured credit facility. The estimated fair values of the Company’s notes were", "bbox": [162.5, 1280.3, 1105.6, 1301.2]}, {"text": "based upon quoted market prices. There has not been any impact to the fair value of derivative liabilities due to", "bbox": [162.5, 1305.3, 1091.2, 1326.2]}, {"text": "the Company’s own credit risk. Similarly, there has not been any impact to the fair value of derivative assets", "bbox": [162.5, 1330.3, 1069.1, 1351.2]}, {"text": "based on the Company’s evaluation of counterparties’ credit risks.", "bbox": [162.5, 1355.3, 716.0, 1376.2]}, {"text": "The fair value of cash and cash equivalents, trade accounts receivable-net and accounts payable", "bbox": [204.2, 1408.6, 1001.6, 1429.4]}, {"text": "approximated book value due to the short-term nature of these instruments at September 30, 2018 and 2017.", "bbox": [162.5, 1433.6, 1065.5, 1454.4]}, {"text": "F-34", "bbox": [617.8, 1484.1, 657.2, 1504.9]}]}